    <title>MAC系统安装gitee步骤</title>
    <url>/2023/08/12/MAC%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85gitee%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、Git下载安装"><a href="#一、Git下载安装" class="headerlink" title="&#x3D;&#x3D;一、Git下载安装&#x3D;&#x3D;"></a>&#x3D;&#x3D;一、Git下载安装&#x3D;&#x3D;</h2><ol>
<li><a href="https://git-scm.com/download/mac">git官网</a>下载git安装包</li>
</ol>
<p>​		点击Binary installer下的 installer选择安装包下载</p>
<p>​		在MAC 客户端 输入<code> git version</code> 查看git是否安装成功</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<ol start="2">
<li>在<a href="https://gitee.com/">gitee官网</a>注册账户并登陆</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="二、配置公钥"><a href="#二、配置公钥" class="headerlink" title="&#x3D;&#x3D;二、配置公钥&#x3D;&#x3D;"></a>&#x3D;&#x3D;二、配置公钥&#x3D;&#x3D;</h2><p>如果不配置公钥，每次上传文件到远程仓库都需要用户名和密码验证。</p>
<p>点击查看<a href="https://help.gitee.com/base/account/SSH%E5%85%AC%E9%92%A5%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE">SSH公钥配置</a></p>
<ol>
<li>复制一下命令，去git终端执行生成 SSH Key：</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight excel"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -<span class="built_in">t</span> <span class="symbol">ed25519</span> -C <span class="string">&quot;181822826@qq.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>注：”Gitee SSH Key”可以任意命名</p>
<p>输出，如：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Generating public/private ed25519 key pair.</span><br><span class="line">Enter file in which to save the key (/home/git/.ssh/id_ed25519):</span><br><span class="line">Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase):</span><br><span class="line">Enter same passphrase again:</span><br><span class="line">Your identification has been saved in /home/git/.ssh/id_ed25519</span><br><span class="line">Your public key has been saved in /home/git/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub</span><br><span class="line">The key fingerprint is:</span><br><span class="line">SHA256:ohDd0OK5WG2dx4gST/j35HjvlJlGHvihyY+Msl6IC8I Gitee SSH Key</span><br><span class="line">The key&#x27;s randomart image is:</span><br><span class="line">+--[ED25519 256]--+</span><br><span class="line">|    .o           |</span><br><span class="line">|   .+oo          |</span><br><span class="line">|  ...O.o +       |</span><br><span class="line">|   .= * = +.     |</span><br><span class="line">|  .o +..S*. +    |</span><br><span class="line">|. ...o o..+* *   |</span><br><span class="line">|.E. o . ..+.O    |</span><br><span class="line">| . . ... o =.    |</span><br><span class="line">|    ..oo. o.o    |</span><br><span class="line">+----[SHA256]-----+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>&#x3D;&#x3D;中间通过三次<strong>回车键</strong>确定&#x3D;&#x3D;</li>
</ul>
<ol start="2">
<li>查看生成的 SSH 公钥和私钥：</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/Users/xiejincheng/.ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>进入上面地址文件夹，找到文件：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">id_ed25519  id_ed25519.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>私钥文件 <code>id_ed25519</code></li>
<li>公钥文件 <code>id_ed25519.pub</code></li>
</ul>
<ol start="3">
<li>&#x3D;&#x3D;用记事本打开<em><strong>公钥文件</strong></em>&#x3D;&#x3D; <code>id_ed25519.pub</code>，复制公钥</li>
</ol>
<p>​	将公钥粘贴到 gitee 后台公钥文本框内，标题命名，如：Python Study</p>
<p>&#x3D;&#x3D;确认公钥是否成功添加&#x3D;&#x3D;，</p>
<p>​	在终端输入</p>
<p>​	<code> ssh -T git@gitee.com</code></p>
<p>​	然后输入：yes</p>
<p>​	显示以下内容，则成功</p>
<p>​	<code>Hi USERNAME! You&#39;ve successfully authenticated, but GITEE.COM does not provide shell 			access.</code></p>
<h2 id="三、新建仓库"><a href="#三、新建仓库" class="headerlink" title="&#x3D;&#x3D;三、新建仓库&#x3D;&#x3D;"></a>&#x3D;&#x3D;三、新建仓库&#x3D;&#x3D;</h2><ol>
<li><p>仓库名称：Python Study</p>
</li>
<li><p>点击创建</p>
</li>
<li><p>输入配置（只需要配置一次，后面不需要再配置）</p>
<p>&#x3D;&#x3D;分别在终端输入执行以下两句代码&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>
<p>Git 全局设置:</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config <span class="attr">--global</span> user<span class="selector-class">.name</span> <span class="string">&quot;ELEVENWORLD&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config <span class="attr">--global</span> user<span class="selector-class">.email</span> <span class="string">&quot;181822826@qq.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="四、下载远程仓库到电脑"><a href="#四、下载远程仓库到电脑" class="headerlink" title="&#x3D;&#x3D;四、下载远程仓库到电脑&#x3D;&#x3D;"></a>&#x3D;&#x3D;四、下载远程仓库到电脑&#x3D;&#x3D;</h2><p>​	Https 和 ssh 都可以，这里我们选择 ssh ,复制地址</p>
<p>​	&#x3D;&#x3D;在终端执行下载命令&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>
<p>​	<code> git clone git@gitee.com:elevenworld/wef.git</code></p>
<p>​	在电脑文件夹 &#x2F;Users&#x2F;xiejincheng 可看到下载的远程仓库文件夹Python Study</p>
<h2 id="五、文件上传至远程仓库"><a href="#五、文件上传至远程仓库" class="headerlink" title="&#x3D;&#x3D;五、文件上传至远程仓库&#x3D;&#x3D;"></a>&#x3D;&#x3D;五、文件上传至远程仓库&#x3D;&#x3D;</h2><p>​	在Python Study放入需要上传的文件</p>
<p>​	 当前终端地址为桌面，在当前终端输入</p>
<p>​	<code>cd Python Study</code></p>
<p>​	&#x3D;&#x3D;将终端地址切换至Python Study文件夹&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>
<p>​	&#x3D;&#x3D;分别输入以下三个命令&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>
<ul>
<li><code> git add .</code>    把所有内容放进暂存区</li>
<li><code> git commit -m &quot;写一句描述该文件夹的信息&quot;</code></li>
<li><code>git push origin master</code></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="六、从仓库下载到电脑"><a href="#六、从仓库下载到电脑" class="headerlink" title="&#x3D;&#x3D;六、从仓库下载到电脑&#x3D;&#x3D;"></a>&#x3D;&#x3D;六、从仓库下载到电脑&#x3D;&#x3D;</h2><p>进入远程仓库，复制https地址</p>
<p><a href="https://gitee.com/elevenworld/phython-study.git">https://gitee.com/elevenworld/phython-study.git</a></p>
<p>将该地址输入终端 即可执行下载远程仓库内文件</p>
<p>在终端输入以下信息：</p>
<p><code> git clone https://gitee.com/elevenworld/phython-study.git</code></p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>gitee</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
